    "body": "More context: when Status detects that you are offline, the send button will be hidden. But, it may happen that you may sent a message before the app knows the device is offline. In that case, the message is lost but marked as \"sent\". Btw, there is no \"resend\" functionality (https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6449).\r\n\r\n@chadyj do you consider it a blocker for release 0.9.30? ",
